This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the lightonai organization:
- lightonai/pagnol-small tokenizer.json (MIT)
- lightonai/pagnol-xl tokenizer.json (MIT)
- lightonai/alfred-40b-1023 tokenizer.json (Apache-2.0)

The `lightonai/alfred-40b-0723` model alias in this package reuses the existing `tiiuae/falcon-7b` tokenizer family and does not bundle an extra tokenizer asset here.

See LICENSE for the full license text that applies to this package and its bundled assets.
